Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the happiness you will have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is so much more than what I received.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakana went back,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Kunad Gate is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yuito...\N-You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create\Na relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone\Nsomewhere to embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here\Nand between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now,\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’ll see I’m always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller coaster\Ninside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and\Nthe unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,THE TWO BROTHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The search team is on the move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But what took them so long to find this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I hacked into the system,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I made some changes to the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I marked the place as "searched."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they are searching from scratch\Nbecause they couldn't find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you undo all the entanglements?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We detected entanglements
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,from 11 years ago and 50 years into the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and from the time when Yakumo was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We untied those entanglements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Yakumo Sumeragi's timeline\Nconnected to the Kunad Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw how he got assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That caused a dimensional entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo was never assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we've never heard of such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't in the history lesson either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not sure either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But we did saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo Sumeragi was assassinated by Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen used the Arahabaki to time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you saying he traveled back in time\Nto when Yakumo was still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure the people you saw\Nwere Yakumo and Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He wore a mask just as the legend says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! It's the mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, tell us what you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why Yakumo was wearing a mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was injured in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he put on that mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he never showed up in public again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There were rumors about him\Nacting like a completely different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,His personality changed? Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Yakumo Sumeragi was murdered\Nby Karen who traveled back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He replaced him under the disguise of that mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So Yakumo was Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Karen is also Yuito's ancestor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He already had children before the injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would Karen do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters now is finding a way\Nto destroy the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If our assumption is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there should be a dimensional entanglement\Nthat formed when Karen time traveled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to undo that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But we found no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The entanglement created by Wakana
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,can only be undone by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The entanglement my brother created\Ncan only be undone by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We must get Karen to Chronos Terminal\Nand make him undo the entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt he would come quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, can you pinpoint Karen's location?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I can't track him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have an idea about where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo Sumeragi is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He is in his slumber right beneath\Nthe Suoh Capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He is bidding his time for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath the Suoh Capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The first place that comes to our mind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Sumeragi crypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is a tourism destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your family's crypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But my brother might have visited it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Chief Sumeragi know Karen\Ncould very likely be Yakumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.\NWe've never met again since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chief has been stripped of his authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been held accountable for leaking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,top-secret information to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He became our scapegoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,NO CONNECTION
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Suoh is in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is our chance to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Kunad Gate still\Nposes a great threat to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll deal with it after we're done with Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time for petty arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You must learn how to treat your own wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Sumeragi, you shouldn't wait for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand firmly on your own legs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for your country New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong, Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a message from my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants me to go there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\Nthe Chief wanted Yuito's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The power you possess
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ability to control gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We need that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When you use your power\Nto shake the Extinction Belt
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and pave the path to Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that's when our revenge is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To shake the Extinction Belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have that kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible with every brain\Nin our country via SAS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even users like us can't handle\Nthe load from SAS!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need is their brains and body parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will track Yuito's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact us as soon as anything comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The reaction is getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kunad Gate has become even more violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the authority\Nto dispatch the OSF troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told you had been grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't being monitored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and take your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the time travel work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no Other in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's settle this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Major General Fubuki told you our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He told me you were trying to gain\Naccess to the Sumeragi crypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Time travel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He even told me Karen was Yakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is beyond absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,These claims are nothing more\Nthan baseless speculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to undo the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lost all authority as the Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am still the head of the Sumeragi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My intention to fulfill Yakumo's\Ndying wish hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,pointing a gun at a power user\Nis probably pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt you would hurt your own brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I am not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of my mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,not even my own brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Others have shown up in the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these the OSF troops from Suoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To think they'd actually find this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, there are too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have just left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But you wouldn't find the crypt if I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But Brother and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:16:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are both our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true Karen traveled back in time\Nand disguised as Yakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Mom from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have a better grasp\Nof the situation of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know by now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,how twisted New Himuka actually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That twist was created by\Nnone other than the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They created the Extinction Belt\Nand send the Others our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,People of Earth suffer because of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroying the Moon is the duty of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We have made great sacrifices for this cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we've deceived the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it was all for the sake of our revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and to realize Yakumo's ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be pointless if everyone dies\Nfor the sake of extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you are just like\Nthe people in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are being shackled by the ancestor\Nyou've never even met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This country is indeed twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The OSF I respected was\Nhiding all kinds of dirty secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I still want to fight as one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want to protect the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow the words of someone\Nfrom over 200 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Create your own future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how my friends and I made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You somehow managed to stop Togetsu's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you've avenged our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done many things\NI wished I could've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have my thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the key to Sumeragi crypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't agree with what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've come this far to prove your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So prove to me that you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you must live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove to me your way is the right one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane and everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt, Chief Sumeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Suoh and Seiran signed a temporary truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A truce...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To stop the destruction brought by Kunad Gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki\Nmanaged to persuade both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito's status as a wanted fugitive\Nhas been rescinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru is back at the headquarters too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They have delayed our punishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but only for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't relax just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The truce means the situation\Nhas gone even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Others detected above Suoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They are large in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The earthquake just now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,knocked out the defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our anti-Other artillery system\Nlost 30 percent of its capacity!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We should head back to Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads into\Nthe ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tomorrow's in your hands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don't tell me now you're afraid♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's no time to waste♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Go forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Have no fear for anything♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Now, let's go♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Into a brand new day♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,INTO THE CRYPT
